<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Ringkasan — Maaf yang Menyembuhkan</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:ital,wght@0,300;0,700;1,300;1,700&family=Outfit:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --ink: #0F0F1A;
  --red: #E94560;
  --teal: #2A9D8F;
  --amber: #E9A030;
  --purple: #8B5CF6;
  --green: #34D399;
  --cream: #FAF7F2;
  --soft: #F2EDE6;
}
*, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
body { background: var(--cream); font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; color: var(--ink); overflow-x: hidden; }

/* HERO */
.hero { background: var(--ink); padding: 52px 24px 48px; text-align: center; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
.hero-bg { position: absolute; inset: 0; background: radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 50% at 20% 50%, rgba(233,69,96,0.18) 0%, transparent 60%), radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 60% at 80% 30%, rgba(42,157,143,0.15) 0%, transparent 60%), radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 40% at 60% 80%, rgba(139,92,246,0.12) 0%, transparent 60%); }
.hero-badge { display: inline-block; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 5px 14px; border-radius: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
.hero h1 { font-family: 'Fraunces', serif; font-size: clamp(32px, 6vw, 52px); color: #fff; line-height: 1.1; position: relative; z-index: 1; margin-bottom: 14px; }
.hero h1 em { color: var(--red); font-style: italic; font-weight: 300; }
.hero-sub { font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45); position: relative; z-index: 1; max-width: 400px; margin: 0 auto 32px; line-height: 1.65; }
.modul-pills { display: flex; gap: 8px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
.m-pill { padding: 7px 16px; border-radius: 30px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; border: 1.5px solid transparent; transition: all 0.25s; font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; }
.m-pill:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); }
.m-pill:not(.active) { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07); border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.12); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); }
.m-pill.active { color: #fff; box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); }
.p1.active { background: #E94560; border-color: #E94560; }
.p2.active { background: #2A9D8F; border-color: #2A9D8F; }
.p3.active { background: #E9A030; border-color: #E9A030; }
.p4.active { background: #8B5CF6; border-color: #8B5CF6; }
.p5.active { background: #34D399; border-color: #34D399; color: #0a2a1a; }

/* BODY */
.body-wrap { max-width: 1040px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 16px 80px; }

/* SECTION */
.section { display: none; }
.section.active { display: block; animation: fadeUp 0.4s ease forwards; }
@keyframes fadeUp { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(16px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }

/* SEC HEADER */
.sec-head { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 28px; }
.sec-num { font-family: 'Fraunces', serif; font-size: 72px; line-height: 0.85; opacity: 0.12; flex-shrink: 0; user-select: none; color: var(--accent, #E94560); }
.sec-kode { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent, #E94560); margin-bottom: 6px; }
.sec-title { font-family: 'Fraunces', serif; font-size: clamp(20px, 3vw, 28px); line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.sec-desc { font-size: 14px; color: #666; line-height: 1.65; max-width: 580px; }

/* INSIGHT */
.insight-strip { background: var(--ink); border-radius: 16px; padding: 22px 26px; margin-bottom: 28px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
.insight-strip::after { content: ''; position: absolute; right: -30px; top: -30px; width: 160px; height: 160px; border-radius: 50%; background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--accent-glow, rgba(233,69,96,0.25)) 0%, transparent 70%); }
.ins-label { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3); margin-bottom: 8px; }
.ins-text { font-family: 'Fraunces', serif; font-size: clamp(15px, 2.5vw, 19px); color: #fff; line-height: 1.5; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
.ins-text em { color: var(--accent, #E94560); font-style: italic; font-weight: 300; }

/* LABEL */
.lbl { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #AAA; margin-bottom: 14px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
.lbl::after { content: ''; flex: 1; height: 1px; background: #E8E2DA; }

/* FLIP GRID */
.flip-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(160px, 1fr)); gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 28px; }
@media (min-width: 560px) { .flip-grid.g2 { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; } .flip-grid.g3 { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; } .flip-grid.g4 { grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); } }
@media (max-width: 559px) { .flip-grid.g3, .flip-grid.g4 { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }

.flip-card { height: 170px; perspective: 1000px; cursor: pointer; }
.flip-card.tall { height: 210px; }
.flip-inner { position: relative; width: 100%; height: 100%; transform-style: preserve-3d; transition: transform 0.55s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0.2, 0.2, 1); }
.flip-card.flipped .flip-inner { transform: rotateY(180deg); }
.flip-front, .flip-back { position: absolute; inset: 0; border-radius: 14px; backface-visibility: hidden; -webkit-backface-visibility: hidden; padding: 16px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
.flip-front { background: #fff; border: 1px solid #E8E2DA; justify-content: space-between; }
.flip-back { background: var(--ink); transform: rotateY(180deg); justify-content: center; }
.ff-top { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; justify-content: space-between; }
.ff-emoji { font-size: 28px; line-height: 1; }
.ff-num { font-family: 'Fraunces', serif; font-size: 26px; line-height: 1; color: var(--accent, #E94560); opacity: 0.25; }
.ff-title { font-weight: 600; font-size: 13px; color: var(--ink); line-height: 1.35; margin-top: 8px; }
.ff-hint { font-size: 10px; color: #BBB; font-weight: 500; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px; margin-top: 4px; }
.fb-label { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent, #E94560); margin-bottom: 8px; }
.fb-text { font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.65; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.78); }

/* ACCORDION */
.accordion { margin-bottom: 28px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
.acc-item { background: #fff; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid #E8E2DA; overflow: hidden; }
.acc-item.open { box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.07); }
.acc-head { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; padding: 14px 16px; cursor: pointer; user-select: none; }
.acc-icon { font-size: 20px; flex-shrink: 0; }
.acc-title { font-weight: 600; font-size: 13px; flex: 1; }
.acc-arr { width: 22px; height: 22px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--soft); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0; transition: transform 0.3s, background 0.2s; }
.acc-item.open .acc-arr { transform: rotate(180deg); background: var(--accent, #E94560); }
.acc-arr svg { width: 11px; height: 11px; }
.acc-item.open .acc-arr svg path { stroke: #fff; }
.acc-body { max-height: 0; overflow: hidden; transition: max-height 0.35s ease; }
.acc-body-inner { padding: 2px 16px 16px 48px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.7; color: #555; }

/* COMPARE */
.compare { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; border-radius: 14px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid #E8E2DA; margin-bottom: 28px; }
@media (max-width: 480px) { .compare { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
.compare-col { padding: 18px; }
.compare-col.bad { background: #1C0808; }
.compare-col.good { background: #091A14; }
.c-label { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 12px; }
.compare-col.bad .c-label { color: #FF8FA3; }
.compare-col.good .c-label { color: #6EE7B7; }
.c-item { font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.6; padding: 6px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05); display: flex; gap: 8px; align-items: flex-start; }
.c-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.compare-col.bad .c-item { color: rgba(255,200,200,0.75); }
.compare-col.good .c-item { color: rgba(180,255,220,0.8); }
.ci { flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }

/* STEP SWITCHER */
.steps-wrap { margin-bottom: 28px; }
.steps-nav { display: flex; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 14px; }
.step-btn { padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; border: 1.5px solid #E0D9CE; background: #fff; color: #888; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s; font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; }
.step-btn.active { background: var(--accent, #E94560); border-color: var(--accent, #E94560); color: #fff; }
.step-panel { background: var(--ink); border-radius: 14px; padding: 22px 24px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; min-height: 130px; }
.step-panel[data-n]::before { content: attr(data-n); font-family: 'Fraunces', serif; font-size: 110px; line-height: 1; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.035); position: absolute; right: 12px; bottom: -10px; pointer-events: none; }
.sp-title { font-family: 'Fraunces', serif; font-size: 18px; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 10px; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
.sp-title em { color: var(--accent, #E94560); font-style: italic; }
.sp-body { font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.62); position: relative; z-index: 1; }

/* TAKEAWAY */
.takeaway { background: var(--soft); border-radius: 14px; padding: 18px 20px; display: flex; gap: 14px; align-items: flex-start; border-left: 4px solid var(--accent, #E94560); margin-top: 8px; }
.tw-icon { font-size: 18px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px; }
.tw-text { font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.7; color: #444; }
.tw-text strong { color: var(--ink); }

/* PROGRESS */
.progress { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 8px; padding: 28px 0 8px; }
.prog-dot { width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; background: #D5CEC5; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.25s; }
.prog-dot.active { width: 24px; border-radius: 4px; background: var(--prog-c, #E94560); }

/* HORSEMAN */
.h-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(220px, 1fr)); gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 28px; }
.h-card { border-radius: 14px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid #E8E2DA; }
.h-head { background: #2C0A0A; padding: 10px 14px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
.h-name { font-weight: 700; font-size: 13px; color: #FF9999; }
.h-emoji { font-size: 16px; }
.h-body { background: #FFF5F5; padding: 12px 14px; }
.h-def { font-size: 12px; color: #555; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.h-cure { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; color: #2A9D8F; background: #E6F7F6; border-radius: 6px; padding: 5px 8px; }

/* 3-col cards */
.triple { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 28px; }
.t-card { background: #fff; border-radius: 14px; border: 1px solid #E8E2DA; padding: 18px; transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s; }
.t-card:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.07); }
.t-icon { font-size: 26px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
.t-title { font-weight: 600; font-size: 13px; color: var(--accent, #E94560); margin-bottom: 6px; }
.t-body { font-size: 12px; color: #666; line-height: 1.65; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg"></div>
  <div class="hero-badge">Ringkasan Materi</div>
  <h1>Maaf yang <em>Menyembuhkan</em></h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">5 modul utama dalam satu tempat. Tap kartu, explore, baca sesantai yang kamu mau.</p>
  <div class="modul-pills">
    <button class="m-pill p1 active" onclick="go(1,this)">01 · Kenapa Nggak Ngefek</button>
    <button class="m-pill p2" onclick="go(2,this)">02 · Otak &amp; Konflik</button>
    <button class="m-pill p3" onclick="go(3,this)">03 · Script Minta Maaf</button>
    <button class="m-pill p4" onclick="go(4,this)">04 · Nerima Maaf</button>
    <button class="m-pill p5" onclick="go(5,this)">05 · Habis Baikan</button>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="body-wrap">

<!-- S1 -->
<div class="section active" id="s1" style="--accent:#E94560;--accent-glow:rgba(233,69,96,0.25);">
  <div class="sec-head">
    <div class="sec-num">01</div>
    <div>
      <div class="sec-kode">Modul 1</div>
      <div class="sec-title">Kenapa "Maaf Lahir Batin" Nggak Pernah Benar-Benar Ngefek</div>
      <p class="sec-desc">Permintaan maaf yang kosong bukan soal kurang tulus. Ada elemen yang kalau dilewat, orang yang menerima tetap nggak bisa beneran merasakannya.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="insight-strip">
    <div class="ins-label">Insight Utama</div>
    <div class="ins-text">Kebanyakan orang hanya menggunakan <em>1 dari 6 elemen</em> yang dibutuhkan agar permintaan maaf bisa benar-benar diterima.</div>
  </div>

  <div class="lbl">6 Elemen Permintaan Maaf · tap kartu untuk penjelasan</div>
  <div class="flip-grid g3">
    <div class="flip-card" onclick="this.classList.toggle('flipped')">
      <div class="flip-inner">
        <div class="flip-front"><div class="ff-top"><div class="ff-emoji">🎯</div><div class="ff-num">1</div></div><div class="ff-title">Pengakuan</div><div class="ff-hint">↩ tap untuk detail</div></div>
        <div class="flip-back"><div class="fb-label">Pengakuan</div><div class="fb-text">Sebutkan secara spesifik apa yang dilakukan. Bukan "atas semua kesalahanku" tapi "waktu aku melakukan X." Tanpa ini, orang tidak tahu maaf kamu untuk apa.</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flip-card" onclick="this.classList.toggle('flipped')">
      <div class="flip-inner">
        <div class="flip-front"><div class="ff-top"><div class="ff-emoji">💥</div><div class="ff-num">2</div></div><div class="ff-title">Dampak</div><div class="ff-hint">↩ tap untuk detail</div></div>
        <div class="flip-back"><div class="fb-label">Dampak</div><div class="fb-text">Tunjukkan bahwa kamu paham apa yang dirasakan orang yang kamu sakiti. Bukan asumsi — tapi pengakuan bahwa efeknya nyata, apapun niatmu.</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flip-card" onclick="this.classList.toggle('flipped')">
      <div class="flip-inner">
        <div class="flip-front"><div class="ff-top"><div class="ff-emoji">🙋</div><div class="ff-num">3</div></div><div class="ff-title">Tanggung Jawab</div><div class="ff-hint">↩ tap untuk detail</div></div>
        <div class="flip-back"><div class="fb-label">Tanggung Jawab</div><div class="fb-text">Tidak ada "tapi". Tidak ada penjelasan yang diam-diam mengalihkan. Kepemilikan penuh atas apa yang terjadi.</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flip-card" onclick="this.classList.toggle('flipped')">
      <div class="flip-inner">
        <div class="flip-front"><div class="ff-top"><div class="ff-emoji">💔</div><div class="ff-num">4</div></div><div class="ff-title">Penyesalan</div><div class="ff-hint">↩ tap untuk detail</div></div>
        <div class="flip-back"><div class="fb-label">Penyesalan</div><div class="fb-text">Diekspresikan dengan cara yang terasa nyata, bukan performa. Orang bisa merasakan bedanya — dan kalau kamu hanya menirukan format, mereka akan tahu.</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flip-card" onclick="this.classList.toggle('flipped')">
      <div class="flip-inner">
        <div class="flip-front"><div class="ff-top"><div class="ff-emoji">🔧</div><div class="ff-num">5</div></div><div class="ff-title">Perbaikan</div><div class="ff-hint">↩ tap untuk detail</div></div>
        <div class="flip-back"><div class="fb-label">Perbaikan</div><div class="fb-text">Tawaran konkret untuk memperbaiki situasi jika memungkinkan. Menunjukkan bahwa maafnya bukan cuma kata-kata.</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flip-card" onclick="this.classList.toggle('flipped')">
      <div class="flip-inner">
        <div class="flip-front"><div class="ff-top"><div class="ff-emoji">🌱</div><div class="ff-num">6</div></div><div class="ff-title">Komitmen ke Depan</div><div class="ff-hint">↩ tap untuk detail</div></div>
        <div class="flip-back"><div class="fb-label">Komitmen</div><div class="fb-text">Satu hal spesifik yang akan dilakukan berbeda. Bukan janji umum "akan lebih baik" — tapi perubahan yang bisa diamati.</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="lbl">Yang terlihat seperti maaf tapi bukan · tap untuk alasannya</div>
  <div class="accordion">
    <div class="acc-item">
      <div class="acc-head" onclick="openAcc(this)"><div class="acc-icon">🚫</div><div class="acc-title">"Maaf kalau kamu tersinggung"</div><div class="acc-arr"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6" stroke="#888" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></div></div>
      <div class="acc-body"><div class="acc-body-inner">Kata "kalau" mengalihkan tanggung jawab ke pihak penerima. Artinya tersirat: mungkin kamu yang terlalu sensitif. Ini pembelaan yang dibungkus format maaf.</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="acc-item">
      <div class="acc-head" onclick="openAcc(this)"><div class="acc-icon">🚫</div><div class="acc-title">"Aku minta maaf, tapi kamu juga..."</div><div class="acc-arr"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6" stroke="#888" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></div></div>
      <div class="acc-body"><div class="acc-body-inner">Kata "tapi" membatalkan semua yang ada sebelumnya. Otak secara otomatis mendiskon apapun sebelum "tapi" dan fokus ke yang sesudahnya.</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="acc-item">
      <div class="acc-head" onclick="openAcc(this)"><div class="acc-icon">🚫</div><div class="acc-title">"Aku sudah minta maaf, apa lagi yang kamu mau?"</div><div class="acc-arr"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6" stroke="#888" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></div></div>
      <div class="acc-body"><div class="acc-body-inner">Permintaan maaf digunakan sebagai alat untuk mengakhiri percakapan dan memindahkan rasa bersalah ke pihak lain.</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="acc-item">
      <div class="acc-head" onclick="openAcc(this)"><div class="acc-icon">🚫</div><div class="acc-title">"Maaf lahir batin" tanpa konteks</div><div class="acc-arr"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6" stroke="#888" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></div></div>
      <div class="acc-body"><div class="acc-body-inner">Formula ritual yang diucapkan semua orang di momen yang sama kepada semua orang. Terasa seperti kewajiban sosial, bukan pilihan yang sadar.</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="takeaway"><div class="tw-icon">💡</div><div class="tw-text"><strong>Yang perlu diingat:</strong> Permintaan maaf yang lengkap bukan soal panjang atau pendeknya. Satu kalimat yang mencakup pengakuan, dampak, dan tanggung jawab jauh lebih kuat dari paragraf panjang yang menghindari ketiga hal itu.</div></div>
</div>

<!-- S2 -->
<div class="section" id="s2" style="--accent:#2A9D8F;--accent-glow:rgba(42,157,143,0.25);">
  <div class="sec-head">
    <div class="sec-num">02</div>
    <div>
      <div class="sec-kode" style="color:#2A9D8F">Modul 2</div>
      <div class="sec-title">Otak Kamu Waktu Konflik Itu Lagi Nggak Bisa Diajak Mikir Jernih</div>
      <p class="sec-desc">Bukan kamu yang lemah. Ada mekanisme biologis yang membuat bagian otak yang berpikir jernih practically offline saat konflik terjadi.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="insight-strip" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0D2B22,#0F1A25);">
    <div class="ins-label">Insight Utama</div>
    <div class="ins-text">Saat konflik, amygdala mengambil alih sebelum prefrontal cortex sempat berpikir. Yang keluar saat itu bukan keputusan sadar — <em>itu reaksi otomatis.</em></div>
  </div>

  <div class="lbl">Dua bagian otak yang bertarung · tap kartu</div>
  <div class="flip-grid g2" style="margin-bottom:28px;">
    <div class="flip-card tall" onclick="this.classList.toggle('flipped')">
      <div class="flip-inner">
        <div class="flip-front"><div class="ff-top"><div class="ff-emoji">🔴</div></div><div class="ff-title" style="color:#E94560;font-size:15px;margin-top:10px;">Amygdala</div><div style="font-size:12px;color:#888;margin-top:6px;line-height:1.5;">Detektor ancaman. Aktif duluan, sering salah.</div><div class="ff-hint">↩ tap untuk detail</div></div>
        <div class="flip-back" style="background:#1C0808;"><div class="fb-label" style="color:#FF9999">Amygdala</div><div class="fb-text">Memproses konflik interpersonal seperti ancaman fisik. Memicu respons fight, flight, atau freeze sebelum kamu sempat berpikir. Ini yang membuat kalimat yang kamu sesali bisa keluar tanpa direncanakan.</div></div>
